    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small, earthwork fortifications in the form of an entrenched earthen rectangle, square, or pentagon that were used mostly in Northern Europe from the late middle ages until the 19th century.</Note_Text>
